# CP Crime — Victim Portal APIs
#
# Works in: IntelliJ HTTP Client · VS Code REST Client · httpyac CLI
# Select environment: vp-dev | vp-sit | vp-preprod | vp-prod
#
# 1. Run "Get Entra Access Token" first.
# 2. Run any request below — token is resolved automatically.

# VS Code: resolves token from the named request response below
@vp_access_token = {{getToken.response.body.$.access_token}}

# @name getToken
### Get Entra Access Token (Client Credentials)
POST https://login.microsoftonline.com/{{tenant_id}}/oauth2/v2.0/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

client_id={{client_id}}&client_secret={{client_secret}}&scope={{scope}}&grant_type=client_credentials

> {%
    client.global.set("vp_access_token", response.body.access_token);
%}

###

# ─── Crime Prosecution Case Details ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Spec: https://app.swaggerhub.com/apis/HMCTS-DTS/api-cp-crime-prosecution-case-details — v1.0.1

# @name getCaseDetailsWaf
### GET Case Details by URN via WAF
GET {{waf_base_url}}/cases/{{case_urn}}
Authorization: Bearer {{vp_access_token}}
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{vp_subscription_key}}

###

# @name getCaseDetailsApim
### GET Case Details by URN via APIM
GET {{apim_base_url}}/cases/{{case_urn}}
Authorization: Bearer {{vp_access_token}}
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{vp_subscription_key}}

###

# ─── Court Schedule ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Spec: https://app.swaggerhub.com/apis/HMCTS-DTS/api-cp-crime-schedulingandlisting-courtschedule — v1.1.0

# @name getCourtScheduleWaf
### Get court schedule by case URN via WAF
GET {{waf_base_url}}/case/{{case_urn}}/courtschedule
Authorization: Bearer {{vp_access_token}}
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{vp_subscription_key}}

###

# @name getCourtScheduleApim
### Get court schedule by case URN via APIM
GET {{court_schedule_base_url}}/case/{{case_urn}}/courtschedule
Authorization: Bearer {{vp_access_token}}
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{vp_subscription_key}}

###

# ─── Case ID Mapper ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Spec: https://app.swaggerhub.com/apis/HMCTS-DTS/api-cp-caseadmin-case-urn-mapper — v1.0.9

# @name getCaseIdByUrn
### GET Case ID by URN via Ingress
GET {{ingress_base_url}}/urnmapper/{{case_urn}}
Authorization: Bearer {{vp_access_token}}

###

# ─── Courthouses ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Spec: https://app.swaggerhub.com/apis/HMCTS-DTS/api-cp-refdata-courthearing-courthouses — v1.1.0

# @name getCourthouse
### Get courthouse by court ID
GET {{courthouses_base_url}}/courthouses/{{court_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{vp_access_token}}
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{vp_subscription_key}}

###

# @name getCourtroomById
### Get courthouse and specific court room
GET {{courthouses_base_url}}/courthouses/{{court_id}}/courtrooms/{{court_room_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{vp_access_token}}
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{vp_subscription_key}}

###
